<title>zhǔ a wǒ de zuǐ chún 迦南332</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ a wǒ de zuǐ chún měi tiān zàn měi nǐ, wǒ de shé tóu měi tiān gē sòng nǐ
 wǒ de shēng mìng dé yǐ cún huó shì yīn nǐ de cí ài hé lián mǐn.
 wǒ yào wǒ yào chuán yáng nǐ de cí ài nǐ de mìng lìng mìng lìng jǐn dōu gōng yì
 shén a wǒ men qū xī jìng bài nǐ pū rén qū xī jìng bài nǐ.
 zàn měi zhǔ shǐ wǒ men dé yī zhì zàn měi zhǔ shǐ wǒ men xīn huān xǐ
 yé hé huá shǐ wǒ men dé yī zhì xíng zǒu a lì shàng jiā lì.</lyrics>
</song>